# Data (PubChem–ADMET processed CSVs)

The processed PubChem–ADMET CSV files exceed GitHub’s per-file size limit (100 MB) and are therefore hosted externally on Google Drive.

**Google Drive folder:**  
https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1YmDrDAioDM_o92VwLHdsJJIRb30usbLN?hl=ko

## Files
Download the following files and place them in this directory (`admet_finetune/data/`):

- `data.csv`
- `data_filtered.csv`
- `data_scaffold_5fold.csv`
